fields.title: Sunnah of morning prayer
fields.description: The Sunnah of Fajr is recited exactly like Fajr. So, in the morning, we perform two units of Sunnah prayer and two units of Fard (obligatory) prayer.
fields.prayer_part2: Mentally, intention can be expressed as follows:
fields.mentally: I intend to perform (a type of prayer)

fields.title: Sunnah of morning prayer
fields.description: The Sunnah of Fajr is read exactly like Fajr. In total, in the morning we read two rakats of sunnah and two rakats of fard.
fields.prayer_part2: Mentally, intention can be expressed as follows:
fields.mentally: I intend to perform (a type of prayer)
